    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Gluss'sa'Nikto, or \"pale nikto\", came from the Gluss'elta Islands of Kintan, causing them to be natural sailors. They have white-gray skin, eye-horns like the kadas'sa'nikto, and fins similar to those of the esral'sa'nikto, but smaller. Xenobiologists believe the first gluss'sa'nikto to have been born of a kadas'sa'nikto who mated with an esral'sa'nikto.</p>",
